Wednesday, December 7, 1994

MERIT DOCKET

94-2223. State ex rel. Chester v. Steiner.

In Mandamus. On motion for summary judgment. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.

AW. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur. Moyer, C.J., would grant the motion for summary judgment.
